                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc type="DonationNote"/>
                           <locus target="#IIv"/>
                           <q xml:lang="la">
                              Donum Papae Leonis XIII Ioh. Bollig. Praefectus Bibl. Vat.
                           </q>
                           <note>
                              The note is written in Latin and states that pope <persName role="bequeather" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6258LeoXIII">Leo XIII</persName> donated the book to the
                              <ref type="ins" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0003BAV">Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana</ref>, in the person of the librarian
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11520JBollig">Johann Bollig</persName>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="ScribalSupplication"/>
                           <locus target="#90r"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ቀውስጦስ፡ ኢ<supplied reason="omitted">ት</supplied>ርስዑኒ፡ በጸሎት።</q>
                           <note>The note mentions <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11523Qawestos">Qawǝsṭos</persName> as the scribe.</note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#133r"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4859Litany">Wa-kāʿba nāstabaqqʷǝʿo la-ʾamlāka mǝḥrat</title>.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ <del rend="strikethrough">
                                 <hi rend="rubric">
                                    <supplied reason="omitted">ዘ</supplied>ማቴዎስ፡</hi>
                              </del>
                              <add place="inline">መልከ፡ ጼዴቅ፡</add>
                              <add place="inline">
                                 <hi rend="rubric">ዘኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</hi>
                              </add> ዘዓጥረየ፡ በንውዩ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡
                              ወዘተዓገሎ፡ ወዘተሣየጦ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ፈቃደ፡ እግዚኡ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በሰ<del>ፈ</del>ይፈ፡ ቃሎሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን፨</q>
                           <note>The note mentions <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11524Matewos">Mātewos</persName> as the owner of the book. His name, written in red,
                              has been struck out with a black line and replaced with those of later owners: <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11525MalkaSe">Malka Ṣedeq</persName>
                              and <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11526HaylaGi">Ḫayla Giyorgis</persName>, the latter written in red.</note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote"/>
                           <locus target="#134r"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ <del rend="erasure">
                                 <supplied reason="omitted">ዘ</supplied>መልከ፡ ጼዴቅ፡</del>
                              <add place="margin">
                                 
                                    <sic>ወውሉዱ፡</sic>
                                  ወልደ፡ ገብርኤል፡</add> ወብእሲቱ፡
                              <add place="margin">
                                 <del rend="erasure">ወለተ፡ ገብርኤል፡</del>
                              </add> ወወለቱ፡ ኤልሳቤጥ፡ ድንግል፡
                              
                                 <sic>ስና<supplied reason="omitted">ይት</supplied>፡</sic>
                               ዘአጥረዮ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ከመ፡ 
                                 <sic>ይኵኖ፡</sic>
                              
                              ለመድኃኒተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወሥጋ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳው<supplied reason="omitted">ሎ</supplied>ስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ 
                                 <sic>ለይኵን።</sic>
                              
                           </q>
                           <note>
                              The note states that <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11525MalkaSe">Malka Ṣedeq</persName> is the owner of the book. It also mentions
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11527WaldaGa">Walda Gabrǝʾel</persName> as his son, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11528WalattaGa">Walatta Gabrǝʾel</persName>
                              as his wife, and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11529Elsabet">ʾElsābeṭ</persName> as his daughter.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#133r"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText"><title cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5069Prayer">Saʾalnāka maḥari saʾalnāka faṭāri</title>.</desc>
                           <note>
                              The blessing is written in another hand. It begins as follows:
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ሰአልናከ፡ መሐሪ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ገባሪ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ወአስተብቋዕናከ፡</q>, and terminates as follows: 
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ወለእመኒ፡ ተገብረ፡ 
                                    <sic>በውስቲቱ፡</sic>
                                  ሕምዝ፡ ወሥራይ፡ በስምከ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ይስዓር፡ ሀበነ፡ ንግበር፡ በሥምረትከ፡ ኵሎ፡ ጊዜ፡
                                 
                                    <sic>ይኵነነ፡</sic>
                                  መብልዓ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ውስቴ፡ ሕይወት፡ ዘበአማን፡ ስብሐቲከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም።</q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>Several names are written in the supplication formulas: that of the first owner is illegible due to erasure. The names of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11524Matewos">Mātewos</persName>,
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11526HaylaGi">Ḫayla Giyorgis</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11525MalkaSe">Malka Ṣedeq</persName>, and
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11530WaldaIM">Walda ʾIyasus Moʾa</persName> (the last only on <locus target="#67r"/>) are written over erasure.
                           </desc>
                        </item>
